They couldn't see me but I heard everything they said.
He proceeded to tell them about some idiot girl who walked in asking if the special was today because she was too stupid to see all the signs.
I almost spit out my sandwich in disgust and I felt really nauseous so I left immediately.
This terrible experience totally killed the great mood I was in that morning.
I will ever come back to this place to be treated like a second class citizen for absolutely no reason.
